    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#gamerules">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        <h3>
        Hearthstone Battlegrounds has <strong>60 bosses</strong> and <strong>143 minions</strong> in total. <br>
        Before each game, each player can select one of the <strong>four</strong> bosses provided, and each boss has its own hero power. The <strong>Tier List</strong> of the heroes is provided in the later section.<br>
        There are <strong>8 players</strong> in each game, and each player has <strong>40 health</strong> <strong>(exceptPatchwerk, who has 55 health due to its hero power)</strong>. <br>
        Players end their game when their bosses have 0 or negative health, and the game is ranked based on the time they knock out.<br>
        There are 2 phases for each round: <strong>Recruit Phase</strong> and <strong>Combat Phase</strong>.
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
