      <li> get 1 coin by selling a minion</li>
      <li> use 1 coin to refresh all minions in the current Tavern</li>
      <li> freeze the Tavern and recruit minions in the next round
      <li> freely rearrange the minions owned</li>
      <li> automatically fuse 3 identical cards to a triple card and obtain a card from the Tavern Tier above(or from Tier 6 if players are at Tier 6)</li>
